title: Townhouse 3 beds, 2.5 baths in Miami
posting_body: ['Great place to call home!', '3/2/1 Townhome in Tropical Park Villas.', 'Home features large, bright and airy living/ dining and tile throughout.', 'All bathrooms have been updated.', 'Impact double doors being installed.', 'Impact windows except for sliding backyard doors (accordion shutters there).', 'New Stainless-steel refrigerator.', 'Second patio off kitchen with washer/dryer room.', 'Tiled backyard with shed.', 'Open balcony off master bedroom.', '2 parking spaces directly in front of unit.', 'Community pool and located across from Tropical Park.', 'Conveniently located to Palmetto Expwy., shopping and within close proximity to FL Turnpike.', 'Fred Ardjmand / One Stop Realty', 'Licensed Sales Associate', 'Direct:', 'show contact info', 'Coral Gables, Coconut Grove, Pinecrest, Palmetto Bay, Dadeland, Brickell and South Miami rental specialist!', 'Listing Courtesy of The Keyes Company']
